The paper discusses visual semantic information pursuit, which is a core task in computer vision applications such as object detection, visual semantic segmentation, visual relationship detection, and scene graph generation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, since the paper also involves visual context reasoning and deep learning, it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
